snippet.title: Global Farmer | Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
GLOBAL FARMER | OUT ON STEAM ON OCTOBER 7th
Based on real-world data from OpenStreetMap, you can play anywhere in the world. Explore your own neighborhood from the perspective of a budding farmer, or try to become a successful agriculture magnate in all
other locations on the planet.
Check it out here: https://links.aerosoft.com/GlobalFarmer
